columnDataChange.oldValue: select org.name as store, org.id as orgid, u.id as salesmanid, u.name as salesmanname, sum(sol.orderedQuantity) as quantity, round(sum(sol.orderedQuantity*(sol.grossListPrice-sol.grossUnitPrice)),2) as totaldiscount, case when round(sum(sol.orderedQuantity*(sol.grossListPrice-sol.grossUnitPrice)),2) = 0 then 0 else ( case when sum(sol.grossListPrice) = 0 then 100 else round((sum(sol.grossListPrice-sol.grossUnitPrice)/sum(sol.grossListPrice))*100,2) end ) end as totaldiscpercentage, round(sum(sol.lineNetAmount + (select sum(taxAmount) from OrderLineTax olt where olt.salesOrderLine = sol)),2) as totalsales, round(sum(tc.cost),2) as totalcost, case when round(sum(tc.cost),2)>0 then round(sum(sol.lineNetAmount + (select sum(taxAmount) from OrderLineTax olt where olt.salesOrderLine = sol))/(sum(tc.cost)),2) else NULL end as markup, round(sum(sol.lineNetAmount + (select sum(taxAmount) from OrderLineTax olt where olt.salesOrderLine = sol)-tc.cost),2) as grossmargin, round((sum(sol.lineNetAmount + (select sum(taxAmount) from OrderLineTax olt where olt.salesOrderLine = sol)-tc.cost)/sum(sol.lineNetAmount + (select sum(taxAmount) from OrderLineTax olt where olt.salesOrderLine = sol)))*100,2) as grossmarginpercentage from TransactionCost as tc join tc.inventoryTransaction as t right join t.goodsShipmentLine as iol left join iol.salesOrderLine as sol left join sol.product as p left join sol.salesOrder as o left join o.salesRepresentative as u left join p.productCategory as pc left join o.obposApplications as posapp left join o.organization as org where o.salesTransaction = 'Y' and o.documentStatus = 'CO' and posapp.client.id=:client and posapp.organization.id IN (:organizationList) and o.creationDate>to_date(:datefrom,'YYYY-MM-DD') and o.creationDate<to_date(:dateto,'YYYY-MM-DD') and @optional_filters@ group by org.name, org.id, u.name, u.id order by totalsales desc, quantity desc, org.name, u.name
